位 0.0, 故障中位 0.4, 变化率 2.0\n     - `pod_processes`: 正常中位 1.0, 故障中位 9.0, 变化率 1.6\n     - `rrt_max` & `rrt`: 延迟增加，变化率超过 1.8\n   - **可能原因:** 可能由于 `recommendationservice` 的某个 Pod 资源消耗激增导致，并伴随显著的进程数量变化，暗示重启或处理异常。\n\n2. **Frontend Service**\n   - **Pod Name:** `frontend-0`, `frontend-1`, `frontend-2`\n   - **异常指标:**\n     - `rrt_max` 和 `rrt`: 延迟明显增加，变化率接近 1.0，在部分时刻甚至超过 2.0\n   - **可能原因:** 前端服务的响应时间显著增加，可能由于下游服务异常或自身负载激增。\n\n3. **Node Memory Usage**\n   - **Node Name:** `aiops-k8s-05`\n   - **异常指标:**\n     - `node_memory_usage_rate`: 正常中位 36.46, 故障中位 36.29, P99 变化率 0.7282\n   - **可能原因:** 虽然变化率较低，但此节点上相关服务出现性能问题，可能由于某些 Pod 的资源消耗。\n\n### JSON 输出\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"pod_processes\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"node_memory_usage_rate\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod CPU usage and process count increased significantly, indicating resource strain or restart.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage increase from 0.0 to 0.4; pod_processes increase from 1.0 to 9.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod CPU usage increased significantly, indicating resource strain or restart.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage increase from 0.0 to 0.4\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod CPU usage and process count increased significantly, possibly due to resource strain or restart.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage increase from 0.01 to 0.4; pod_processes increase from 1.0 to 9.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Response time spikes across multiple pods indicating service degradation.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max increases from 116764 to 389865\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-05\",\n      \"reason\": \"Memory usage remains stable, but associated pods show performance issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate P99 change ratio 0.7282\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
